Name: Cybercube battle
About the game: Single-player battle royale game. The goal of the game is to remain the only survivor. Every 60 seconds the circle narrows. In order not to die, you must keep in a circle. A choice of 5 characters. Several types of firearms. (machine guns, pistols, shotguns, sniper rifles) There are also melee weapons. (axes, knives, machete)
